{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Birates!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game, you\u2019ll gather resources, craft gear, and battle waves of enemies as you try to survive. By day, explore the island and prepare; by night, fight against powerful enemies. Whether you play solo or team up with friends, every choice matters in your fight for survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Craft, Build, Survive</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/CraftGif.gif?t=1736557756\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather resources and craft essential tools and weapons. Build your arsenal by chopping trees, mining, and hunting for materials. Your survival depends on the gear you create.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Choose Your Own Build</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/BuildGif.gif?t=1736557756\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from a variety of random upgrades and power-ups as you gain experience. Shape your playstyle with unique abilities and powerful boosts each time you level up.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Dynamic Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/DungeonCorrect.gif?t=1736557756\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine melee and ranged attacks, and unleash abilities tied to your gear for fast-paced, action-packed combat. And when you feel ready, challenge the powerful bosses that lurk under the island for the ultimate test of your skills.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Survive Together in Co-op</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269650/extras/Together.jpg?t=1736557756\" /></p><p